<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3085] Importing/exporting &quot;.&quot; should not be allowed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3085</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the Equinox implementation of OSGi, importing and exporting the default package (&quot;.&quot;) is allowed, whereas it fails to produce the expected results under Apache Felix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12520101">FELIX-3085</key>
            <summary>Importing/exporting &quot;.&quot; should not be allowed</summary>
